event.title: English Japanese Dictionary
event.description:
English to Japanese Dictionary with offline feature.
Download this largest Japanese dictionary with over 1 lakhs of word meaning.
This Dictionary have favorite word marking to get useful word immediately.
This have 3 types of Game to test your Vocal Level.
1. Japanese to English Game
2. English to Japanese Game
3. Fill in Blank Game with Japanese Hint

English to Japanese Dictionary have word of day feature to show daily word meanings for you with notification. You can turn on or off this feature anytime from setting.
